dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Benjamin Hughes. May I have your name, please?
Hi there, my name is Lori Smith.
Nice to meet you, Lori. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's three one two four eight.
Thank you, Lori. I also need your date of birth for verification purposes. When were you born?
I was born on the twenty first of March, nineteen eighty five.
Great, thank you for the information. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today, Lori?
I'd like to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, Lori. I'll be happy to assist you with that. Thank you for reaching out to us. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
Thank you for your time. Have a wonderful day, Lori. Goodbye!
